## hostname: cb-xserve01.mozilla.com
## uname: Darwin cb-xserve01.mozilla.com 8.9.1 Darwin Kernel Version 8.9.1: Thu Feb 22 20:55:00 PST 2007; root:xnu-792.18.15~1/RELEASE_I386 i386 i386
